Q: Tell me about yourself
A: I am a software developer with 3 years of experience in backend engineering.
Good answer. Add measurable achievements.

Q: Why do you want to work at Google?
A: I admire Google's mission and believe I can grow by contributing to impactful projects.
Great motivation, try connecting it to your skills.

Q: What is your greatest strength?
A: My greatest strength is problem-solving under pressure.
Clear strength. Give an example to support it.

Q: Describe a challenge you overcame at work
A: I once led a failing project back to success by reorganizing team workflows.
Strong story. Include what you learned.
